實」，並表示中方在釣魚台的立場一貫明確，釣魚台自古以來就是中國固有疆域，中國對釣魚台的主權有充分的歷史和法理依據，維護釣魚台主權的決心堅定不移。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/日本今更名釣魚台-陸官媒徹底崩潰了-083013406.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BB%8A%E6%9B%B4%E5%90%8D%E9%87%A3%E9%AD%9A%E5%8F%B0-%E9%99%B8%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92%E5%BE%B9%E5%BA%95%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0%E4%BA%86-083013406.html&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=c69c5891\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/日本今更名釣魚台-陸官媒徹底崩潰了-083013406.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:22:59.000Z","msg":"自古以來地球陸地都係一塊過<br />\n即係地球上的領土都是終國的<br />\n地殼移動先係分裂終國的元兇"},{"pid":"d641c09c59b0dac7bae4f17a5b075e5bb0972acd","tid":2074660,"uid":252605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a2f312b831541e909ee6a65f316c03dfaf9cd2d","tid":2074660,"uid":121255,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:35:56.000Z","msg":"直接派遼寧號去佔島啦<br />\n<br />\n反正南海仲裁都無視左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係驚日本仔阿？又話領土缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:23:20.000Z","msg":"支持!!<br />\n國土不容侵犯呀!<br />\n<br />\n不過... 遼寧號去到咁遠? 嗰邊D 風浪好大架喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29248d2206d7cf56f9d4d45afe9d1917d2b9dc4a","tid":2074660,"uid":266342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"自古以來支那就是賤種的一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54ed57cb90edb1cf7db1d8350a321fd5f0f25b6","tid":2074660,"uid":155682,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"602f42023faa63f2c4f757758448ad8741551249","tid":2074660,"uid":79563,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"37c058ee5054d754ff910e90de3759c28005aa3d","tid":2074660,"uid":174601,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:28:11.000Z","msg":"🤪蒙古又係唔係自古以來既領土<br />\n<br />\n打